casebody.data:
NATIONSTAR MORTGAGE, LLC, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Tedd W. GUENZEL, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Mrs. Tedd W. Guenzel, his wife, and TD Bank, N.A., Defendants. C-731 September Term 2018
081993 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000912-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
